Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.16,0:00:09.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イカサマ シゴロ賽を\N見破ったカイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.17,0:00:12.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, seeing through the loaded dice, catches Foreman Ohtsuki out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.17,0:00:12.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ついに班長 大槻を追い詰める
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:17.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,500)\pos(640,505)}Applause, And...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.37,0:00:23.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No way! You've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:23.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じょ… 冗談じゃない\Nそんなこと！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.01,0:00:25.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 筋は通っている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.38,0:00:25.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No, that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.36,0:00:33.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,積み重ねてきたロジック
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:38.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's logic makes sense to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.76,0:00:36.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,理はワシが見る限り
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.59,0:00:40.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君にある
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.26,0:00:43.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だ… 誰だ あんたは！\N一体なんの権利があって…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.39,0:00:42.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.23,0:00:43.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Where do you get off—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.67,0:00:45.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こら！口を慎め 大槻！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:46.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Shut up, Ohtsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.97,0:00:48.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このお方は帝愛グループ\N最高幹部の一人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.12,0:00:52.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This man is on Teiai Group's board! Second only to our great leader President Hyodo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.71,0:00:51.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,偉大なる総帥\N兵藤会長の次に位置する
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.71,0:00:54.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この王国のナンバー２
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.02,0:00:57.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This kingdom's number two! You're talking to Yoshihiro Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.41,0:00:56.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黒崎義裕様であられるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.88,0:01:00.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええっ！\N控えろ！控えろ 控えろ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.16,0:01:00.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Back off! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.55,0:01:03.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,消し飛ぶぞ！\Nお前のようなゴミクズ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.84,0:01:03.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Get out of here, you scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.42,0:01:09.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This man can send you to far deeper, crueler pits than this one just by pointing a finger!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.45,0:01:05.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この方の指先ひとつで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.42,0:01:09.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この地下よりも\Nさらに過酷な地下の地下まで！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.13,0:01:11.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,控えろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.42,0:01:10.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So back off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.43,0:01:17.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,も… 申し訳ございません！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:19.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry! Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:19.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お許しを！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.21,0:01:29.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいかな？その賽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.22,0:01:29.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Can I see those dice?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.32,0:01:34.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.35,0:01:35.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どれ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.42,0:01:38.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん　何かの骨だな これは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.45,0:01:38.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,These are made out of bone, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.66,0:01:41.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは奴が\Nこれ見よがしに食っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.82,0:01:43.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Bones from the T-bone steaks he ate in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:43.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,Ｔボーンステーキの骨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.06,0:01:49.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そいつをトイレで少しずつ削って\Nサイコロの形にし
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:49.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We shaved them down using the toilets into the shape of dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.47,0:01:52.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ピンの赤は俺の血をすり込んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.59,0:01:52.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The red dots are our blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.81,0:01:58.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフッ なるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:57.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.14,0:02:00.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なるほど フフッ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.17,0:01:59.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.74,0:02:04.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大槻とやら　仕方ないな これは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.79,0:02:04.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ohtsuki didn't leave you any other choice, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.58,0:02:06.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は絡め取られたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.62,0:02:07.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You've been caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.92,0:02:09.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が今まで\Nここの連中にしてきたように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.04,0:02:14.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Netted by a thorough plan just like the one you've been springing on the inmates here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.89,0:02:14.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,綿密に用意 計画され\N絡め取られた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.30,0:02:18.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So you can dish it out but you can't take it, I see?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.33,0:02:18.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,他人にはするが\N自分がされた時は ご免こうむる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:21.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,通らないだろ\Nいくらなんでも それは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.66,0:02:21.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's just no good at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.58,0:02:27.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You only use the loaded dice on a dealer's second turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:24.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この親２回に限っては
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.13,0:02:27.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,特殊賽を仲間内で回して使う
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:29.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ということで\N勝負を続行するしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.25,0:02:29.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That way people can't avoid them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.64,0:02:32.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黒崎様　勘弁してください！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.95,0:02:32.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Please, Mr. Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.01,0:02:36.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この金は 私がコツコツ\N営々 蓄えてきた汗の結晶でして
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.26,0:02:36.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've poured blood, sweat, and tears into saving up this money!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.91,0:02:40.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それをこんな こんな必ず負けると\N知っているギャンブルで…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.97,0:02:40.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't lose it all on a bet I'm guaranteed not to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:44.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いやいや そうとは限らんぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.92,0:02:43.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Now that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:48.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かにこの勝負\Nシゴロ賽を使えば負けは必至
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.62,0:02:51.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If you use the 4-5-6 dice you're sure to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.76,0:02:51.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,100パーセント負ける勝負だが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:54.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,普通の賽を使えば\N引き分けの目は出てくる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:55.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But if you use normal dice, you can draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.83,0:02:57.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,216分の１ほどの確率で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:57.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You've got 1-in-216 odds.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:59.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,く… 黒崎様
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:00.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:03:02.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここは潔く\Nそれに懸けるしかあるまい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.02,0:03:03.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Man up and roll the dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.67,0:03:04.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黒崎様　それはあまりに…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:05.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kurosaki! That's too—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:06.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こら！往生際が悪いぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:06.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't you know when to give up!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.64,0:03:09.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだそうだ！\Nやれ 大槻！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:08.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:09.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Roll 'em, Ohtsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.11,0:03:11.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっさとやれよ！\Nどうした どうした！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:10.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:11.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.65,0:03:15.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言ってたじゃねえか お前\N念じる力で目が出るんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.84,0:03:13.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It was your own idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.76,0:03:16.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You can make the dice come up how you want just by thinking about it, right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:18.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだそうだ！\Nやってみろ　やれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.02,0:03:17.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:18.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So go ahead and do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:21.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,石和…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.91,0:03:19.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Isawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.29,0:03:23.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沼川…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.35,0:03:22.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Numakawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.30,0:03:34.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この夜のチンチロ勝負\N大槻 対 カイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:37.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The late-night chinchiro duel between Ohtsuki and Kaiji approaches its end!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:38.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ついに決着の時を迎える
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:41.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even Ohtsuki cannot resist Kurosaki's judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.04,0:03:41.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黒崎の審判とあっては\N大槻もあらがえず
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:43.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仕方なく普通の賽を取る
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.46,0:03:43.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,With no choice, he takes up normal dice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:47.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,His prayer, snake eyes and a miraculous draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.98,0:03:47.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,願いは引き分けとなる\N奇跡のピンゾロ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.74,0:03:56.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But he is not so fortunate! His roll is a 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:54.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし そんな調子のよいことは\Nそうそう起こるはずもなく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:56.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出目は３
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:04:01.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然 負ける
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.66,0:04:00.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He loses, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:03.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He loses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.43,0:04:05.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負ける　負ける
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:05.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He loses!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.17,0:04:09.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負ける！負け続ける！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:06.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He loses!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.77,0:04:09.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He keeps losing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:15.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And he coughs up the dirty money he'd squirreled away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:15.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして吐き出す！ここまで\N蓄えてきた汚れた金ほとんどを
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:19.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All that remains in his safe is 1,800 perica!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.28,0:04:19.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結局 金庫に残ったのは\Nたった1800ペリカ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:25.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ohtsuki is crushed! The biggest defeat in underground chinchiro history!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:26.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大槻 大敗！\N地下チンチロ史上最大 歴史的大敗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:29.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一方 カイジらは\N目のくらむような大勝！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.38,0:04:30.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, on the other hand, has scored a dazzling victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.96,0:04:33.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,合計 1825万2000ペリカ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:33.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A total of 18,252,000 perica!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:38.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一人頭 およそ304万ペリカ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:37.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Around 3,040,000 perica each!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:41.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Impossible... Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.20,0:04:41.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカな… バカな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.47,0:04:43.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.64,0:04:47.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんで こんな\N夢みたいなことが 現実に
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:47.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is like a dream! It can't be real!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.29,0:04:50.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Why? Why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.34,0:04:49.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ… どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.23,0:05:07.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ 均等に山分け？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.94,0:05:07.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So we split it evenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:09.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:12.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ　この金は\N４５組の６人で均等に分けるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.36,0:05:12.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All six of us 45s split it even.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:15.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でもカイジさんが\N一番 頑張ったんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.63,0:05:18.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You did most of the work, Kaiji. No one's going to mind if you—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:18.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少しくらい多く取っても\N誰も文句は…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:20.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なーに言ってんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:20.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:24.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この金は みんなで何ヵ月も\N頑張って手にした給料が元手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.66,0:05:24.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We all killed ourselves for months earning the money we started with
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.41,0:05:29.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな金に差別も区別もあるかよ\Nみんな平等だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.77,0:05:29.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't give myself extra out of that money. We're all even.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:30.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほんとに いいんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:31.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You sure!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.95,0:05:35.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たり前だ\Nカ… カイジさんは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.25,0:05:32.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.07,0:05:36.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:38.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんて… なんていい人なんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.15,0:05:38.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're such a great guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:42.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おいおい 逆だって\Nいい人は お前らのほうだって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:42.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No, no! It's all you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.87,0:05:46.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんな何も言わずに\N黙って ついてきてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:46.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You kept quiet and went along with my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:48.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今回の勝ちのネタを\N一切 聞こうとせず
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.25,0:05:51.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You didn't need to hear anything about how I was going to win, you just believed in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.81,0:05:51.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺を信じて ついてきてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.54,0:05:54.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's not an easy thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.54,0:05:54.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なかなか\Nできることじゃねえよ それ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:57.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,普通は聞き出そうとするって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.78,0:05:59.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Most people would ask. It was a lot of money, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.28,0:05:59.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大金が懸かってるんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:02.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けど お前らはそれをしなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.94,0:06:04.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But you didn't. I couldn't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.15,0:06:04.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あり得ないんだよ そんなこと
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:08.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だからこそ\Nそれが決定的勝因になった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.89,0:06:08.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And really, that's why we won.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.19,0:06:10.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝因？\Nそうさ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.41,0:06:09.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Why we won?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:15.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah. That's what really tripped the Foreman up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:13.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの班長が今回\N一番 見誤ったのは
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:15.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさにその点なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:18.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人は人を手放しに\N信じたりしないってのが
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.88,0:06:20.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A guy like him just can't understand people believing in each other like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:22.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴の考えの根幹 常識
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:21.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:29.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So I knew he'd be wrong about why you didn't react when he didn't use the 4-5-6 dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:25.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だからこそ 第１投で\Nシゴロ賽を使わないことへの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.58,0:06:29.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんなの無反応を\N奴は100パーセント誤解した
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.25,0:06:33.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シゴロ賽は気づかれていないと\N誤解した
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:32.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That he'd assume we didn't know his trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:37.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのミスジャッジがなけりゃ\N今回のこの大勝ちはない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:37.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Without that misjudgment, we wouldn't have won like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:41.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんなの俺への信頼が\N勝ちを引き寄せた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.40,0:06:41.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Your trust in me was what let us win!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.19,0:06:45.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Really, guys. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.19,0:06:45.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから みんなには\Nほんとに感謝してるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.06,0:06:46.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.06,0:06:47.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:53.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ ちょ… ちょっと大将\Nん？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.24,0:06:52.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:56.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大将\Nワシのことか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.56,0:06:54.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:56.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You mean me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.41,0:07:00.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,帰っちまう前に約束してくれ\Nそこの外出券の項目には
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.55,0:06:58.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Promise me before you leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:02.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Do something about that one condition on the furlough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:03.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気持ち悪い１文が\Nくっついてるじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:06.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１日50万ペリカで出すかどうかは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.43,0:07:10.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The 500,000 perica part is fine, but the "judgment of Teiai" thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:10.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,帝愛が適正と判断した場合に\N限るとかなんとか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:14.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,んん… そういうことになるな\Nそれが？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:14.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, that? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:17.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せっかく ここまで\Nもってきたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:17.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Look at how far we've come!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.03,0:07:21.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,変な難癖つけずに\Nすんなり出してくれんだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.15,0:07:20.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You can't keep us in here on some weird technicality!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:24.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君\Nこれは難癖とかではなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.31,0:07:25.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, this isn't just a technicality.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.97,0:07:27.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここでの しきたりとして\N落ちて１年未満の者は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.19,0:07:30.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No one leaves this pit during their first year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.87,0:07:29.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出したりしないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.87,0:07:32.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,時期尚早ということでな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:32.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's simply not time yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:42.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,が まあしかし ここまで\N大ごとになったら そうもいくまい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.84,0:07:41.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But I suppose we have to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:46.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今ここで 君らのその願いを\N無下に突っぱねると
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.36,0:07:48.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If we grant that wish of yours right here, right now, it wouldn't be fair to the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:48.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,他の者の手前 よろしくない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:51.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全体の労働意欲に影響する
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.87,0:07:51.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We can't have it reducing their will to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:54.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ…\N認めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.64,0:07:52.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:55.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Very well. Do as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:56.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,好きにするがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.22,0:07:57.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:58.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やった！\Nカイジさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:07:58.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.20,0:08:03.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし出てどうするつもりだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:03.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But what do you plan on doing on the outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:09.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Fifteen million perica. Three million each.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.94,0:08:09.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,約1800万\N一人ずつ割れば300万ペリカ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.29,0:08:12.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's 300,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.31,0:08:12.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日本円に直せば30万だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:14.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこから１日出るなら５万
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.29,0:08:14.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,50,000 of that goes to the furlough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:19.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２日なら10万引かれ\N手にする金は20万か25万
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.83,0:08:19.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,100,000 if you stay out for two days. You'll only have 200,000 or 250,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:22.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それっぽっちの金で\N１日２日 外に行き
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:24.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What can you do in a day or two with that little money?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:24.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしようというのだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:29.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あるのか？1000万近い借金を\N返済する当てでも
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.86,0:08:29.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Can you really repay almost ten million with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.43,0:08:31.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あるさ！ある
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:31.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course I can! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:34.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,というと？\Nギャンブルだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.85,0:08:33.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And how?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:39.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll gamble! If I can win fifty times that 200,000 in two days, there's my ten million!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:36.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２日出て20万
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.14,0:08:40.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その金を50倍にすれば1000万
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:45.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それができなかったから お前らは\N今ここにいるんじゃないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:44.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Remember, you're here because you couldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.72,0:08:49.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ 分からん男だな カイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:49.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't understand you, Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:53.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君はバカか利口か分からん男
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:53.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't tell if you're a fool or a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:56.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし まあいい\N好きにしたまえ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:59.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Very well. Do as you will. We'll meet again in a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:58.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,また会おうじゃないか 数日後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:02.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐らくは またここで フフフッ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:02.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here again, if I'm correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:04.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クッ ふざけるな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.43,0:09:04.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No fucking way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:08.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一度出たら\N誰が戻るかよ こんなとこ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.95,0:09:08.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Who the hell would come back here once they get out!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.07,0:09:11.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll win... I'll win because I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:11.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝ってやる\N死にものぐるいで勝って
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:14.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝って勝って 勝って獲得する
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.49,0:09:12.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll win! I'll win!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:16.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll win back my freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.14,0:09:16.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必ず自由を！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:48.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Light! Sunlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:48.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日だ　日の光だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:52.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji is reborn! Freed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:51.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ 生還！解放される
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:56.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,過酷な地下暮らしの収容所から\N一時的に
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.03,0:09:56.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Freed, for a moment, from his cruel torment beneath the earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.85,0:10:01.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きれいな水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.95,0:09:59.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Clean water...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.43,0:10:03.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Fresh air...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:03.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,新鮮な空気
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.15,0:10:07.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.26,0:10:08.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:09.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There it is! My money!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:11.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ある！金
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:14.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Real money! Yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.50,0:10:14.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本物の金　日本円
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:15.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:18.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やった！帰ってきた この世界に
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:18.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm back! Back in the real world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:21.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji feels bliss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.98,0:10:21.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ 至福の時
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:24.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが しかし！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:24.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But! But!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.17,0:10:34.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,At that moment, the countdown begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:34.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この瞬間から\Nカウントダウンが始まる！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:38.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,動き出す　カイジのシャバでの\N残り時間を示す
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.62,0:10:40.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The watch counting down Kaiji's time out the outside begins to tick!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:41.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,時計が！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:45.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10 11 12 13 14 15 16
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:45.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hundred, 110, 120, 130, 140, 150, 160...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.57,0:10:48.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,17 18 19 20
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.82,0:10:50.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,170, 180, 190, two hundred, 210, 220, 230...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:50.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,21 22 23…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:52.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,託す？\Nはい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.70,0:10:51.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait, extra?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.72,0:10:54.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes. We all talked it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.14,0:10:54.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実は みんなで\N話し合っていたんです
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:11:01.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We thought you might win big, so we all chipped in a bit more for you to bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.68,0:10:58.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし今回の博打が\N思いもかけない大勝ちになったら
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:11:01.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その金をカイジさんに託して\N勝負してもらおうって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:03.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:06.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ？\N別行動で20万を1000万にするより
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:10.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We're more likely to win having you bet than each trying to turn 200 thou into ten million!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:08.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさんに預けて\N勝負してもらうのが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:10.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一番 確率が高いんです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.66,0:11:14.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカ言うな！\N1000万あれば自由になれるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:18.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dumbass! Who the hell do you think's gonna risk it after they've got their 10 mil?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:18.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰が危険を冒して\Nお前らの分まで勝とうとするかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:20.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You guys are really easy marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:20.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お人よしも いい加減にしろ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.17,0:11:23.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お言葉ですが カイジさんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:26.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait, didn't you say before we should split it all evenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:26.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと分け前もらっていいのに\N均等なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:31.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たち同様 お人よしっていうか\Nちょっと抜けてるっていうか…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:30.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're just as bad as us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.48,0:11:34.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ いや！\N単なるお人よしだったら
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.51,0:11:36.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, if that's all you were, we wouldn't have given you our money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:36.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちの大事な金\N託したりしませんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.95,0:11:38.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん\N人がいいだけじゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.97,0:11:42.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You may be a nice guy, but you're... I dunno. Clever, or sharp, or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.99,0:11:42.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,したたかっていうか\N切れるんです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:45.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,間違いなく この中で\N一番勝つ確率の高い人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:45.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're the one of us most likely to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.96,0:11:49.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なーに言ってんだよ！\N分かるか そんなこと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:49.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Seriously? What the hell are you talking about!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:52.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃ あのネタ教えてくださいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:52.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then tell us how you did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.34,0:11:55.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら ３ヵ月前\Nみんなで決起した夜に
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:57.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Three months ago, when we all got together! You guessed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:57.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさんは\N言い当てたじゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:12:00.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Guessed that the Foreman would roll a 4-5-6!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:12:00.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,班長の出目をシゴロだって
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:05.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, it wasn't a sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.51,0:12:05.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれって今考えたら\N絶対シゴロってわけないですよね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:08.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シゴロ賽でシゴロが出る確率は\N２割くらい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.33,0:12:08.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even with the 4-5-6 dice, the odds of an actual 4-5-6 are only about one in five.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:11.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,外れる可能性のほうが高かった
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:11.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You were more likely to be wrong than right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.42,0:12:14.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,外したら どうするつもりでした？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:14.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What would you have done if you were wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:15.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:16.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,同じだ\N同じ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.84,0:12:16.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The same thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:21.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仮にシゴロでなくても\Nその目は４４５とか５５６とか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:24.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even if he didn't roll a 4-5-6, it would've been something close like a 4-4-5 or 5-5-6.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.60,0:12:24.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かなりシゴロに近い目に\Nなっている
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.53,0:12:28.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういう外し方は\Nそれはそれで信用を勝ち取れる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.66,0:12:28.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That near of a miss would have been enough to make you believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:30.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこ！\Nえ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:29.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:33.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういうところ！\Nお人よしプラスその抜け目なさ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:34.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's what it is! You're a nice guy, but then you've got that sharp edge!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:37.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,乗らせてください その博才に！\Nお願いします！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.09,0:12:37.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Teach us how to gamble like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.43,0:12:35.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:40.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,780. 790. Eight hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.38,0:12:40.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,78 79 80
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.18,0:12:45.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして1800万ペリカ\N日本円にして180万を
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.33,0:12:45.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And thus 18,000,000 perica—1,800,000 yen—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:50.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,20日外出する権利と\N80万の現金に振り分けたのだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:50.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,were split into twenty days of furlough and 800,000 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:13:00.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつらときたら お人よし\Nバカどもだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.01,0:12:59.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Those idiots really think I'm a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:02.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:06.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソッ おかげで ますます\N負けられなくなったじゃねえか！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:05.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Now I really can't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:08.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He is tasked with a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:08.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,課せられたのは奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:13.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A miracle beyond his victory in underground chinchiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.91,0:13:13.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの地下チンチロ以上の大勝\Nそんなミラクル
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.65,0:13:16.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジは その元金80万を
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:22.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji has 20 days to turn 800,000 yen into over 60 million, enough to buy freedom for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:21.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,20日間で６人分の借金に当たる\N6000万強にしなければならない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:24.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正確には6075万
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.03,0:13:24.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The total, 60,750,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.66,0:13:28.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's pointless playing around in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.83,0:13:28.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな お遊びカジノじゃ\N話になんねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:31.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…\N気をつけろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:31.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Jeez, watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:33.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:33.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ　悪い
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:41.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Legal gambling isn't gonna get me there. I've gotta go to the underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:41.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,表はダメだ　裏だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.44,0:13:44.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Somewhere where I can figure out their game.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:44.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つ仕組みを築いている所
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:47.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまりイカサマを\N仕組んでいるような所
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.43,0:13:47.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That is, somewhere that's cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:50.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな仕組みがあるってことは
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:53.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,In a shady place like that, I know I can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.02,0:13:53.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逆にその裏さえ突けば 必ず勝てる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:54.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:56.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,兄さん\Nあ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:55.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:14:00.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You look pretty loaded. How's 'bout sharin' the wealth?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:14:00.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ずいぶん持ってるじゃないの\N少し回してよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.43,0:14:07.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おとなしく渡せば\N刺したりなんかしねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.49,0:14:06.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Cough up and I ain't gonna hafta cut ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:09.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大ごとだぞ　刺したら
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:09.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You sure you want to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:13.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ？\Nお前らの顔 覚えたからな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.34,0:14:13.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've seen your faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.61,0:14:16.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,多勢に無勢　ここでやられても
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:19.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You may have me outnumbered here, but we'll find you, tie you up...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:19.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あとで捜し出して\N全員 事務所に監禁し
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:21.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死ぬほど後悔させてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.70,0:14:21.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And give you something worse than death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.91,0:14:26.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We'll lop 'em off one by one. Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:24.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１本１本 落としてやろうか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:26.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなふうに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:31.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Holy shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:31.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤ… ヤバいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.66,0:14:34.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,す… すみませんでした！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:34.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:43.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヘヘヘッ\Nうまくしのいだな 兄さん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.64,0:14:43.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Good job weaseling out of that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.06,0:14:48.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But the real thing doesn't stick their fingers back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.14,0:14:46.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなふうに\N指を取ったり くっつけたり
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.04,0:14:48.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほんまモンが やることやない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:51.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今のはハッタリ\Nあんた 偽モンだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.56,0:14:51.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That was a bluff. You're a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:54.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰だ お前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.94,0:14:53.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.18,0:14:57.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安心せえ　ワシはなんもせんて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:57.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'm not gonna do anything to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.09,0:14:59.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや むしろ逆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:14:59.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:15:03.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいしのぎ方だったと\N感心しとるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.30,0:15:02.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That trick of yours was pretty impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.18,0:15:06.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You may be a good pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:06.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたなら頼めるかもしれんな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:09.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How about it? Wanna go in with me on something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.83,0:15:09.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうよ　組まんか ワシと？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:14.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There's this interesting casino I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:14.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,面白いカジノへ連れていってやる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.50,0:15:16.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Why don't we go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.50,0:15:17.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ついといで　よかったら
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:36.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've been looking for the right young guy in these casinos for the past three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:31.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,探しとったがよ　３日ほど
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.96,0:15:35.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いろんなカジノを回って\N使えそうな若モンを
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:38.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これが なかなかいなくてな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:38.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The right type is hard to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.42,0:15:42.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But I can tell you're it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.66,0:15:41.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが あんたからは感じたんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.70,0:15:44.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何がなんでも勝とうってオーラ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.01,0:15:47.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That aura of wanting to win at anything, whether it's legal or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.03,0:15:48.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのためだったら 犯罪だって\Nいとわないって気配 面構え
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:50.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That expression on your face. I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.57,0:15:51.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気に入ったよ フッ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.31,0:15:52.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.37,0:15:54.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここだ\Nえ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.50,0:15:58.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,An ordinary, unassuming building!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.58,0:15:58.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこは なんの変哲もない\N普通のビル
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.88,0:16:05.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's Sakazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:05.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,坂崎です
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.76,0:16:29.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.81,0:16:29.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.62,0:16:37.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほんとにカジノだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.71,0:16:37.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It really is a casino!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:49.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かにカジノ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:54.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A casino, indeed! A high-stakes illegal casino!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.47,0:16:54.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかも とんでもない高額が\N乱れ飛ぶ 裏カジノ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:16:58.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And there's more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:59.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして さらに！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:01.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.48,0:17:03.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な… なんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.10,0:17:05.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,These are... Pachinko machines!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.18,0:17:05.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは… パチンコ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.68,0:17:08.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カジノでパチンコ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:07.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Pachinko machines in a casino!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.95,0:17:12.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,面白かろう？これが\Nこのカジノの売りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.01,0:17:12.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Interesting, huh? This is this casino's draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.82,0:17:15.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,24時間営業の高レートパチンコ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:15.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,24-hour, high-rate pachinko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:18.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,通常のパチンコは１玉４円
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.89,0:17:18.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Normal pachinko is 4 yen a ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:21.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここはそれの10倍の40円
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.78,0:17:21.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Over here, it's ten times that, 40 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.46,0:17:24.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あるいは100倍の\N400円の台まである
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.61,0:17:24.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And here, it's 400 yen, 100 times normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:26.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,100倍？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.84,0:17:26.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,100 times!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:30.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うおっ！\N来た？来たー！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:29.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:30.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There it is!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:32.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ あれは？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:31.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.68,0:17:37.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's the real draw. The king of all pachinko machines
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.81,0:17:38.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここの目玉のパチンコ台\N裏パチすべての王 頂点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:41.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's 1000 times the normal bet. Each ball is 4,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.31,0:17:42.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,1000倍台　１玉4000円のパチンコ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.45,0:17:44.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Each ball is 4,000 yen!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.59,0:17:44.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１玉4000円？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.54,0:17:56.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.70,0:17:59.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来て！来てくれ　頼む！頼む！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:17:58.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Please! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.50,0:18:04.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヘヘヘヘッ\Nあの台に限り デジパチではなく
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:07.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And that's not a computerized machine. It's an old-style jackpot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:06.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,昔ながらの一発台でな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:11.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほれ あの台の最後の難関\N３連クルーンをかいくぐって
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:15.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If you drop a ball through the three trays at the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.95,0:18:15.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一番下の奥にある 当たりに入れば
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:20.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You win all the balls previous losers have dumped in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:20.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今まで積み上げてきた敗者の玉を\N一気に獲得できる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.46,0:18:25.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり奴が座っている\Nあの足元の玉すべてを
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.73,0:18:25.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All the balls he's sitting on right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.30,0:18:31.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すべてって！あの玉の１つ１つが\N4000円なんだろ？一体いくらに…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.47,0:18:27.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All of them!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:29.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Each ball is 4,000 yen, right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:31.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How many are there!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.05,0:18:35.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Each of those trays holds about a hundred million's worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.10,0:18:34.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの横線の１本ごとに約１億だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:39.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり今 出たら約５億5000万か
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.15,0:18:39.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So the jackpot right now is about 550 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:40.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,500 million!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:41.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,５億！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:52.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He made it to the second tray!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:51.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やった！２段目にも入った！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.92,0:18:54.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,５億！５億だ 来い！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.03,0:18:55.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,500 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:58.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,300万のカードを もう５枚\N1500万もつぎ込んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:59.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've put five three-million cards in! That's 15 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:00.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう限界！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.04,0:19:00.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm almost bust!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:03.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おおっ ３段目だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:03.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The third!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.17,0:19:05.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これが最後！最後だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.29,0:19:05.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is it! This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:07.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来てくれー！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:07.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.40,0:19:09.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来るんだー！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:09.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:28.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sir. You're out of balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.19,0:19:27.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お客様　玉切れですが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.74,0:19:35.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Aww, he almost had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:37.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,惜しかったのになあ\Nどうかお引き取り願います
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:37.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm going to have to ask you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.47,0:19:40.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お客様　お引き取りを
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.60,0:19:40.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sir. You need to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:46.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出ない 出ない　そう簡単には
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:46.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You can't hit the jackpot that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:50.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに あと一歩\Nあともう一歩で出そう！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:50.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But one or two more balls and he may have had it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.45,0:19:52.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ってとこまでは いくがな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:52.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Maybe, just maybe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.38,0:19:55.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とんでもない　性悪さ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.60,0:19:55.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What terrible luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:20:02.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This machine loves to taker you right up to the edge without paying out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.82,0:20:04.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出そうだが決して出ないのが\Nこいつの特徴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.03,0:20:08.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沼　人食い沼だよ こいつは
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.06,0:20:08.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The bog... This is the man-eating bog!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:11.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The jackpot is 500 or 600 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:11.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出れば５億６億
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.30,0:20:15.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ついにベールを脱いだ\N究極のモンスターマシン
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:15.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The veil of the ultimate monster machine is lifted!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.27,0:20:18.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沼！人食い沼！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.45,0:20:19.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The bog! The man-eating bog!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:41.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Most people would ask. It was a lot of money, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.52,0:20:59.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But you didn't. I couldn't believe it. And really, that's why we won.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.51,0:28:24.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜改ざんＢ－ＣＡＳカードによる\N不正視聴は➡
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.18,0:28:27.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,刑法により禁じられた犯罪行為＞
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.70,0:28:30.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜５年以下の懲役 または➡
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.18,0:28:32.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,50万円以下の\N罰金に処せられます＞
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.69,0:28:37.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜後悔しても 元には戻せない＞
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.54,0:28:39.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不正視聴!?
